{"tha-ap105:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap105:0.2":"Bhikkhadayivagga ","tha-ap105:0.3":"Uppalahatthiyattheraapadana ","tha-ap105:1.1":"“Tivarayam nivasiham, ","tha-ap105:1.2":"ahosim maliko tada; ","tha-ap105:1.3":"Addasam virajam buddham, ","tha-ap105:1.4":"siddhattham lokapujitam. ","tha-ap105:2.1":"Pasannacitto sumano, ","tha-ap105:2.2":"pupphahatthamadasaham; ","tha-ap105:2.3":"Yattha yatthupapajjami, ","tha-ap105:2.4":"tassa kammassa vahasa. ","tha-ap105:3.1":"Anubhomi phalam ittham, ","tha-ap105:3.2":"pubbe sukatamattano; ","tha-ap105:3.3":"Parikkhitto sumallehi, ","tha-ap105:3.4":"pupphadanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap105:4.1":"Catunnavutito kappe, ","tha-ap105:4.2":"yam pupphamabhiropayim; ","tha-ap105:4.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap105:4.4":"pupphapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap105:5.1":"Catunnavutupadaya, ","tha-ap105:5.2":"thapetva vattamanakam; ","tha-ap105:5.3":"Pancarajasata tattha, ","tha-ap105:5.4":"najjasamasanamaka. ","tha-ap105:6.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap105:6.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap105:6.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap105:7.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma uppalahatthiyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap105:8.1":"Uppalahatthiyattherassapadanam tatiyam. "}